                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p>Push-ups are a fantastic exercise for building strength, but doing the same routine can get boring. That’s why <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/push-up-variations" target="_blank" rel="noopener">push-up variations</a> are key to keeping things fresh and challenging. One exciting option is the grasshopper push-up.</p><p>This variation works your upper body, targets your core, and improves coordination. It also helps increase flexibility. This makes it a well-rounded exercise. This guide will show you how to do grasshopper push-ups with proper form.</p><p>You’ll discover tips to adjust the exercise for your fitness level and learn how to include it in your routine.</p>                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
